WEBVTT

00:01:31.289 --> 00:01:34.940
[Our Dazzling Days]

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:37.660
[Episode 3]

00:01:44.229 --> 00:01:45.560
What are you looking at?

00:01:47.430 --> 00:01:48.840
Why are you sitting in my seat?

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.700
Ms. Tong asked us to switch seats.

00:01:52.789 --> 00:01:53.430
Why?

00:01:54.070 --> 00:01:55.930
She wants me to be your insulator.

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:56.850
Be what?

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:59.390
Ms. Tong told me to be your insulator.

00:02:08.740 --> 00:02:09.410
Be quiet.

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:15.280
Can you focus on your studies?

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:20.250
You're back?

00:02:27.750 --> 00:02:29.360
Xia Lei, come out for dinner.

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:31.570
Didn't you promise
you wouldn't tell the teacher?

00:02:31.570 --> 00:02:32.190
You promised.

00:02:32.190 --> 00:02:33.910
Why did you go back on your word?

00:02:33.910 --> 00:02:36.030
I didn't tell your teacher

00:02:36.030 --> 00:02:37.400
about the relationship between you two.

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:39.020
I just reminded her

00:02:39.050 --> 00:02:40.700
not to let anything develop between you.

00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:42.300
Now my seat has been changed.

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:46.960
Hurry up. We're waiting for you.

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:47.710
Dinner's ready.

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:48.570
I'm not eating!

00:02:49.150 --> 00:02:50.310
Come out and eat now!

00:02:50.310 --> 00:02:51.520
I'm on a hunger strike!

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:53.150
Hunger strike?
Like that's something to be proud of?

00:02:53.150 --> 00:02:54.430
Let me tell you something, Xia Lei.

00:02:54.430 --> 00:02:56.430
If you start dating someone

00:02:56.430 --> 00:02:57.400
and it affects your studies,

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:58.030
I'll jump off a building!

00:02:58.030 --> 00:03:00.690
Then you and your father
can live by yourselves!

00:03:02.060 --> 00:03:03.260
What's wrong, honey?

00:03:03.710 --> 00:03:04.590
He just won't listen!

00:03:04.590 --> 00:03:05.400
If you do that,

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.560
what will I do?

00:03:06.710 --> 00:03:08.150
We can't punish adults

00:03:08.150 --> 00:03:09.250
for a child's mistake.

00:03:09.250 --> 00:03:10.110
Hunger strike!

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:11.710
I'm innocent!

00:03:11.730 --> 00:03:13.450
I'll take you both with me when I jump.

00:03:13.450 --> 00:03:15.450
Then I'd rather stay with the kid.

00:03:15.880 --> 00:03:16.880
Get out of here.

00:03:21.470 --> 00:03:24.120
Honey, where are you going?

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:30.140
Honey, how could you slam the door?

00:03:30.140 --> 00:03:30.910
Honey!

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:32.710
Come out!

00:03:32.710 --> 00:03:34.360
I'm kicking the door down, honey!

00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:35.420
What are you doing?

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:37.520
Are you coming out or not?

00:03:39.140 --> 00:03:40.800
It almost bumped into me!

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:41.710
Are you crazy?

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:42.400
Stop it!

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:43.880
Stop messing around!

00:03:44.590 --> 00:03:45.360
You spoiled him!

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:46.290
Stop hitting me!

00:03:46.710 --> 00:03:47.840
Lei! Lei! Come out quickly!

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:48.470
-Come out and save me!
-You spoiled him!

00:03:48.470 --> 00:03:49.030
You spoiled him!

00:03:49.030 --> 00:03:50.630
Come save your dad, Lei!

00:03:50.870 --> 00:03:52.130
Why are they fighting?

00:03:53.310 --> 00:03:54.170
Let me tell you.

00:03:54.230 --> 00:03:56.400
My mom's been
getting more and more ridiculous lately.

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:58.000
She went to school and told Ms. Tong

00:03:58.000 --> 00:03:59.240
that I'm dating Meng Ge.

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:01.640
Now the whole class thinks we're together.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.520
Wait. When did you start dating?

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:06.050
What's that supposed to mean?

00:04:06.050 --> 00:04:07.110
You're not dating?

00:04:08.190 --> 00:04:09.870
I was actually
gonna ask you about it recently.

00:04:09.870 --> 00:04:11.520
I noticed you and Meng Ge
are always together,

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:12.680
acting all cozy…

00:04:12.970 --> 00:04:13.940
Do you like her?

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.870
I'll push you off the second floor!

00:04:15.870 --> 00:04:17.360
Stop! I'll fall!

00:04:17.829 --> 00:04:19.560
How dare you grab me! Just wait!

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:20.560
Getting rough with me, huh?

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:22.390
-Get away!
-Are you getting rough with me?

00:04:22.390 --> 00:04:23.600
Harder!

00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:28.430
Getting physical, are you?

00:04:28.430 --> 00:04:29.950
Is Xiaoman here?

00:04:30.630 --> 00:04:31.120
Ma'am!

00:04:31.390 --> 00:04:33.000
Come open the door for me.

00:04:33.070 --> 00:04:33.530
Come on.

00:04:33.870 --> 00:04:34.630
Ma'am.

00:04:35.450 --> 00:04:36.510
Freshly cut seaweed strips.

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:37.630
Look at this kid.

00:04:37.630 --> 00:04:39.120
Coming through the window again.
Use the door.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.120
It's convenient.

00:04:40.510 --> 00:04:41.440
What's going on?

00:04:41.510 --> 00:04:44.440
Using the door means I have to
take the stairs, ma'am.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.360
Xiaoman,

00:04:45.500 --> 00:04:47.190
your knife skills are impressive!

00:04:47.190 --> 00:04:48.720
It's a waste
that you don't sell mixed dishes.

00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:49.510
-Look at this knife skill.
-Right?

00:04:49.510 --> 00:04:50.560
My knife skill has always been like this—

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:51.070
never declined at all.

00:04:51.070 --> 00:04:52.430
Don't chat with them.
Let's go out and have some fun.

00:04:52.430 --> 00:04:53.430
We're eating at home today.

00:04:53.430 --> 00:04:54.720
Come home for dinner later.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:55.580
Did you hear me?

00:04:55.670 --> 00:04:57.730
Um, ma'am, we won't be eating at home.

00:04:58.310 --> 00:04:58.920
No way.

00:04:59.159 --> 00:05:00.120
Dinner is already prepared.

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:00.950
If you two don't eat,

00:05:00.950 --> 00:05:02.550
you're not allowed to go out.

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:02.800
Right.

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.430
You can't go out without eating, Xia Lei.

00:05:04.430 --> 00:05:05.430
-You're not hungry?
-Hurry up.

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:06.430
Not hungry at all?

00:05:06.430 --> 00:05:07.920
-You two…
-Ma'am, he's not hungry.

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:08.720
But he still needs to eat.

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:09.750
You were so obedient when you were little.

00:05:09.750 --> 00:05:10.270
And now,

00:05:10.270 --> 00:05:11.930
you all have minds of your own.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.360
No one leaves without eating!

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:14.160
Do you hear me?

00:05:18.420 --> 00:05:19.020
Go, go, go.

00:05:19.430 --> 00:05:20.020
Hurry up.

00:05:22.190 --> 00:05:22.950
They're gone.

00:05:22.950 --> 00:05:23.800
What's with these kids?

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:24.930
They've gone quiet.

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:26.680
Come on, let's eat.

00:05:28.070 --> 00:05:28.560
Hurry!

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:29.750
It's raining!

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:33.480
Let's go play over there.

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:34.310
It's actually raining.

00:05:34.310 --> 00:05:34.840
Let's go.

00:05:37.950 --> 00:05:38.600
Alright.

00:05:39.430 --> 00:05:40.830
Don't look so miserable.

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:42.040
Look at you.

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:44.040
You just changed seats.

00:05:44.040 --> 00:05:45.370
But those who don't know

00:05:45.620 --> 00:05:47.159
might think Meng Ge went back to Beijing.

00:05:47.159 --> 00:05:48.480
Will you ever stop?

00:05:49.159 --> 00:05:50.560
I've already told my mom

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:51.430
not to go to school

00:05:51.430 --> 00:05:52.360
and tell Ms. Tong about this.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.190
And now,

00:05:53.190 --> 00:05:55.120
the whole class thinks I like Meng Ge.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:56.390
How can I not be angry about that?

00:05:56.390 --> 00:05:57.120
So what?

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:59.430
You want to like her secretly?

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:00.630
Wh-What are you talking about?

00:06:00.630 --> 00:06:02.230
What do you mean "secretly"?

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:05.050
I know what you mean.

00:06:05.510 --> 00:06:09.380
Your mom promised not to do this,

00:06:09.650 --> 00:06:11.320
but she went back on her word.

00:06:11.490 --> 00:06:12.290
And then,

00:06:12.320 --> 00:06:13.750
she went to school

00:06:13.770 --> 00:06:15.960
and told the teacher about it,

00:06:15.980 --> 00:06:18.780
causing the teacher and the whole class

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:20.890
to think you like Meng Ge.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:22.260
That's why you're upset.

00:06:22.260 --> 00:06:23.670
Right.

00:06:26.210 --> 00:06:26.790
But...

00:06:27.490 --> 00:06:28.880
With your attitude toward your mom—

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:30.140
forget about your mom,

00:06:30.190 --> 00:06:31.850
if you acted like this with me,

00:06:31.910 --> 00:06:33.570
I'd think something was up too.

00:06:33.570 --> 00:06:35.690
So I should have calmly told my mom,

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:37.600
"Mom, it's not what you think.

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:40.000
I just borrowed
Meng Ge's poetry collection

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:40.750
and copied some of it.

00:06:40.750 --> 00:06:41.950
I think her poetry is good.

00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:43.190
That's why I copied it.

00:06:43.190 --> 00:06:44.310
It's not what you imagine.

00:06:44.310 --> 00:06:45.720
I don't like Meng Ge,

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:47.000
and Meng Ge doesn't like me either."

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.320
I should have just
calmly explained it to her, right?

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:49.730
Exactly. See? You got worked up again.

00:06:49.730 --> 00:06:51.590
Just talk things through calmly.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:52.480
Right?

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:54.159
Young love like this

00:06:54.159 --> 00:06:56.760
often starts with sharing poetry,
doesn't it?

00:06:56.890 --> 00:06:58.670
Besides, after all these years,

00:06:58.670 --> 00:07:00.870
don't you know your mom's personality?

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:02.270
What kind of person is your mom?

00:07:02.270 --> 00:07:04.720
Anything that might
affect her son's studies

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:06.600
gets completely eliminated.

00:07:06.910 --> 00:07:09.350
Right? Not even a sprout can remain.

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:13.490
Understand now?

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:14.820
I understand.

00:07:15.970 --> 00:07:17.540
[Teaching Building]

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:33.680
I saw a poem at Meng Ge's place yesterday,

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:35.240
and I thought it was pretty good.

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:36.390
What took you so long?

00:07:36.390 --> 00:07:37.190
You're here pretty early.

00:07:37.190 --> 00:07:38.850
You're quite early, Xiaoman.

00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:40.240
Well, I copied it down.

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:41.190
-Take a look. This one.
-Go ahead.

00:07:41.190 --> 00:07:42.190
"To the Oak Tree."

00:07:43.430 --> 00:07:44.240
This one is great!

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:45.430
Why didn't I think of this?

00:07:45.430 --> 00:07:45.920
Right?

00:07:46.310 --> 00:07:48.120
But I'm worried
the teacher
might think it's not appropriate.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:50.430
Because it's all about romance.

00:07:51.070 --> 00:07:52.270
I don't think so.

00:07:52.270 --> 00:07:54.510
Isn't this promoting women's independence?

00:07:54.510 --> 00:07:55.890
Men and women on equal footing.

00:07:55.890 --> 00:07:57.270
Neither is subordinate to the other.

00:07:57.270 --> 00:07:57.830
Right?

00:07:58.300 --> 00:07:59.030
That's good.

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:01.360
Yesterday I divided it up.

00:08:01.380 --> 00:08:03.460
Look, I'll read this part,

00:08:03.490 --> 00:08:04.900
and this part is yours.

00:08:05.070 --> 00:08:06.720
Mine, yours.

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:08.020
And then together.

00:08:08.500 --> 00:08:09.270
How does that sound?

00:08:09.270 --> 00:08:09.760
Not bad.

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.800
Shall we give it a try?

00:08:13.430 --> 00:08:15.220
If I love you,

00:08:15.750 --> 00:08:17.630
I will never be a lovesick bird,

00:08:17.960 --> 00:08:20.790
repeating
the same dull song for your shade.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:23.830
Nor will I be a spring,

00:08:24.130 --> 00:08:27.530
offering cool comfort year after year.

00:08:31.770 --> 00:08:33.490
If I love you,

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:36.120
I will never be

00:08:37.419 --> 00:08:38.809
a trumpet vine,

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:42.820
clinging to your lofty branches
to show myself off.

00:08:43.030 --> 00:08:44.510
If I love you,

00:08:45.090 --> 00:08:46.090
I will never be...

00:08:46.270 --> 00:08:51.080
I will never be a lovesick bird,

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:55.580
repeating
the same dull song for your shade.

00:08:57.060 --> 00:08:58.660
Nor will I be a mountain,

00:08:59.940 --> 00:09:01.400
heightening your stature

00:09:01.970 --> 00:09:03.600
and dignity.

00:09:04.030 --> 00:09:05.080
Not sunlight.

00:09:05.630 --> 00:09:07.000
Not spring rain.

00:09:07.870 --> 00:09:10.030
No, these are not enough.

00:09:10.630 --> 00:09:13.550
I must be a kapok tree,
standing beside you.

00:09:13.910 --> 00:09:15.790
As trees...

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:17.840
We stand together.

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:20.730
Our roots tightly intertwined underground,

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:23.510
and our leaves touching in the clouds.

00:09:33.310 --> 00:09:33.790
You're here.

00:09:33.790 --> 00:09:34.080
How did it go?

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.210
Where have you been?

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:37.030
I went to help my grandma close her stall.

00:09:37.030 --> 00:09:39.460
Xia Lei said you memorized it all.

00:09:40.030 --> 00:09:41.610
Of course I can remember
those couple of lines.

00:09:41.610 --> 00:09:42.730
Come on. Let's go.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:43.600
I told you.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:44.600
He came prepared.

00:09:45.750 --> 00:09:48.150
If I love you,

00:09:48.260 --> 00:09:50.490
I will never be a lovesick bird,

00:09:50.550 --> 00:09:54.070
repeating
the same dull song for your shade.

00:10:44.570 --> 00:10:45.790
What are you doing?

00:10:45.790 --> 00:10:47.200
You're gasping for air.

00:10:48.150 --> 00:10:48.870
I'm fine.

00:10:50.750 --> 00:10:52.210
We all have to wait for him.

00:10:52.630 --> 00:10:55.160
Go ahead and eat.
It'll be wasted if you don't.

00:10:56.930 --> 00:10:57.520
Xiaoman.

00:10:57.880 --> 00:10:59.790
-Why isn't Wang Dongdong here yet?
-Xiaoman?

00:10:59.790 --> 00:11:00.500
Xiaoman!

00:11:00.750 --> 00:11:01.610
Zhang Xiaoman!

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:02.600
Xiaoman!

00:11:03.390 --> 00:11:05.390
Hurry up. Ms. Dai is looking for you.

00:11:05.660 --> 00:11:06.970
Ms. Dai is looking for you!

00:11:06.970 --> 00:11:07.570
What for?

00:11:08.100 --> 00:11:09.300
Come on. It's urgent.

00:11:09.690 --> 00:11:10.910
I just saved a seat.

00:11:10.910 --> 00:11:11.440
Hurry up!

00:11:11.510 --> 00:11:12.640
Keep the seat for me.

00:11:14.670 --> 00:11:15.930
-What is it?
-Let's go.

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:16.870
I don't know.

00:11:16.940 --> 00:11:18.340
The show will start soon.

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:22.390
She's inside.

00:11:22.390 --> 00:11:23.120
Ms. Dai.

00:11:23.550 --> 00:11:24.150
What's wrong?

00:11:24.150 --> 00:11:25.550
"You have your copper branches
and iron trunk."

00:11:25.550 --> 00:11:26.750
What's the next line?

00:11:28.730 --> 00:11:30.680
"Like a knife, a sword, or a halberd."

00:11:30.680 --> 00:11:31.680
Wh-What's wrong?

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:33.200
Ms. Dai, see?

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:34.870
I told you he memorized it.

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:36.360
When we were practicing,

00:11:36.390 --> 00:11:37.670
he was right there beside us.

00:11:37.670 --> 00:11:38.960
What happened to your voice?

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:40.350
Xia Lei lost his voice.

00:11:40.510 --> 00:11:43.570
I gave him some licorice tablets,
but they didn't work.

00:11:43.810 --> 00:11:44.690
Zhang Xiaoman,

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:46.860
can you step up in this emergency?

00:11:47.270 --> 00:11:48.080
Me?

00:11:48.890 --> 00:11:50.960
I haven't even practiced this.

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:52.110
Wait, I...

00:11:52.770 --> 00:11:53.910
It's up to you now.

00:11:59.080 --> 00:12:00.210
It's starting soon.

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:01.150
Where's Xia Lei?

00:12:01.570 --> 00:12:02.690
Don't be nervous.

00:12:02.950 --> 00:12:03.880
Want some water?

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:07.150
Xia Lei...

00:12:07.270 --> 00:12:08.790
I think I just saw him.

00:12:09.030 --> 00:12:10.290
He should be here soon.

00:12:10.670 --> 00:12:12.200
Isn't he usually reliable?

00:12:17.610 --> 00:12:18.540
Here he comes.

00:12:44.270 --> 00:12:45.870
Is there time to try again?

00:12:58.510 --> 00:12:59.040
Yes.

00:12:59.710 --> 00:13:00.270
Yes?

00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:26.030
If I love you,

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:28.870
I will never be a trumpet vine,

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:32.460
clinging to your lofty branches
to show myself off.

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:35.030
If I love you,

00:13:35.790 --> 00:13:37.690
I will never be a lovesick bird,

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:41.290
repeating
the same dull song for your shade.

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:45.360
Nor will I be a spring,

00:13:45.750 --> 00:13:48.240
offering cool comfort year after year.

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:50.840
Nor will I be a mountain,

00:13:51.270 --> 00:13:52.730
heightening your stature

00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:54.550
and dignity.

00:13:55.440 --> 00:13:56.550
Not sunlight.

00:13:57.360 --> 00:13:58.510
Not spring rain.

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:01.460
No,

00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:03.670
these are not enough.

00:14:09.860 --> 00:14:13.100
I must be a kapok tree,
standing beside you.

