Aaron Kwok's haircut?

00:20:47.940 --> 00:20:48.940
Is this right?

00:20:49.440 --> 00:20:51.200
First guy in our plant
with Aaron Kwok's haircut, right?

00:20:51.200 --> 00:20:51.550
Show-off.

