Okay.

00:26:21.520 --> 00:26:23.040
I have a good grandson.

00:26:26.260 --> 00:26:28.910
Sometimes I think

00:26:28.930 --> 00:26:29.610
your father

00:26:30.820 --> 00:26:32.880
couldn't have really abandoned you.

